high_descs: Turn left and head to the counter top the is directly to the left of the stove
Open the cabinet that is above the counter and pick up the green cup then close the cabinet
Turn right and walk to the stove

Open the microwave above the stove and place the green cup inside to the right of the coffee mug then close the microwave and turn it on. Open the microwave and pick up the green cup then close the microwave
Take a couple steps to stand in front of the counter to the right of the stove.
Open the cabinet above the counter and place the green cup inside on the right hand side.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated cup in a cabinet

high_descs: Go left and walk towards the counter next to the stove and look up.
Open the cupboard door to take out the green cup and shut it.
Bring it down and turn to your right and go towards the stove. Bring the cup up to the microwave.
Place the green cup inside the microwave next to the white mug and turn it on. Take the cup back out and shut the door.
Bring it back down and turn left and a quick right back up to the cupboard.
Place the cup back in the cupboard and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a green cup to put it back in the cupboard.

high_descs: Turn to your left and go forward to the counter immediately left of the stove.
Open the right hand cabinet above the counter and get out the green glass.
Move to the front of the stove.
Heat the glass in the microwave above the stove.
Go back to the cabinet where the glass was stored.
Put the glass away in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated green glass in a cabinet.
